{"article_id":"95I2tCBjpMBTFnCW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As supporters and opponents of Proposition 8 , the controversial California measure","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"banning same-sex marriage ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"sifted through the arguments","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"made before the Supreme Court Tuesday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"they could agree on one thing :","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"This is a watershed moment .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"\" I can ' t believe","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"we have come this far , frankly , \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"says Nowlin Haltom , a real estate agent in the Los Angeles suburb of Studio City .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"He married his partner of 15 years in New York two years ago","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"and says","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"he has been in this fight \" for a long time . \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Meanwhile , Tim Wildmon , president of the American Family Association , says","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"the Supreme Court is considering toying with thousands of years of human history .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"\" There is nothing in the history of the world culture","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that supports redefining marriage as an institution between a man and a man or a woman and a woman , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"he says .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Possible outcomes from Tuesday ' s arguments range from the case being dismissed all the way up to a broad ruling","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"on whether or not there is a constitutional right","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"for same-sex couples","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"to marry ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"says Rebecca Brown , a constitutional law professor at the University of Southern California 's Gould School of law .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"\" They ' ve heard all the arguments ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"now they will go away","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and sort through them , \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"she says .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"A decision is expected by early June .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Mr. Haltom is grateful for the progress","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that has been made on the issue ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"when he first came out to his family ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"\" my father would not speak to me for two years. \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The fact","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that the law is being heard in the nation ' s highest court","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"is promising ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"but there is still much work left to do ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"says Haltom , a Vietnam veteran .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" I am certainly hopeful","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that the court will go all the way","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and make the biggest statement , \"","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"he says .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"But \" something more narrow is probably likely . \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"He worries about his own relationship .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"At the moment , his husband would not be allowed to collect Haltom 's Social Security check","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"when Haltom dies .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Prior to his current marriage , he was married to a woman","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"with whom he has a grown daughter .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"\" My ex-wife is entitled to claim my benefit check , \"","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"he adds .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"But Haltom says","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"he is braced for any outcome","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and will continue his work regardless .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"There is much work left","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to do","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"with the next generation of activists ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"he notes .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"A Prop . 8 rally","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"held at Los Angeles City Hall on Sunday","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"drew no more than 350 supporters ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"he says .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" In a city of this size , don ' t you think","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"we should have gotten a better showing than that ? \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Mr. Wildmon suggests","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that a broad Supreme Court ruling in support of same-sex marriage would fly in the face of the clear majority opinion in America .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Though polls now show","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that more than 50 percent of Americans support same-sex marriage ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"he notes","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that 31 states have created legislation","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"defining marriage as being only between a man and a woman .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Some indications from the court Tuesday suggest","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that it might be wary of making a broad ruling ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"says Paul Linton , special counsel at The Thomas More Society , a national anti-abortion and anti-gay marriage advocacy group in Chicago .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"For example , Justice Anthony Kennedy said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"the plaintiffs were asking the court to head into \" uncharted waters . \"","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"\" I would be very concerned about the negative impact","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that [ a broad ] decision would have not just in California but across the entire nation , \"","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Mr. Linton says .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":83,"text":"He suggests","depth":4},{"id":84,"text":"that such a decision could lead to some states","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"calling for a constitutional amendment ,","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"meaning Congress might have to convene a convention .","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"\" It has never been used in our history \" since the original Constitutional Convention of 1789 ,","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"he notes .","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"if two-thirds of the states demanded it ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"he adds ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"it could happen .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":170,"right":184,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":109,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":104,"right":108,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":98,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":94,"right":95,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":9,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":12,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":13,"right":106,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":118,"right":168,"relat